<HEADLINE>
FT  25 MAR 93 / UK Company News: Ricardo
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
The impact of a Pounds 650,000 property provision cut profits at Ricardo
Group, a provider of engineering and technological services, from Pounds
1.21m to Pounds 875,000 pre-tax for the half year to December 31.
Turnover from continuing operations improved to Pounds 31.7m (Pounds 28.6m)
and operating profits by 24 per cent to Pounds 1.77m.
Pre-exceptional earnings from continuing operations amounted to 3.09p
(2.48p) per share. The interim dividend is maintained at 1.9p.
