<HEADLINE>
FT  24 MAR 93 / London Stock Exchange: New Highs and Lows for 1992/93
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NEW HIGHS (79).
AMERICANS (1) Cont'l. Bank, CANADIANS (1) Can. Pacific 4pc Deb, BREWERS (2)
