(Dollars million)
 -------------------------------------------------------------
Motion pictures               0       25      100      175
Television                  200      175      200      175
Cinema chain                 25       25       25       35
Sub total                   225      225      325      385
Corporate overheads         -75     -100      -75      -75
Operating profit            150      125      250      310
